{"tid":1787523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國網民：既然香港想要5大訴求，就贏他們5球！","createTime":"2019-12-18T03:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T05:49:44.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6129583b54dd29f823420586161e697c24d1da2c","tid":1787523,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:44:38.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】國足今日將在東亞盃賽最後一場分組賽大戰港隊，教練李鐵賽前憶起職業生涯最美好時刻。<br />\n<br />\n國足於今日東亞盃將對港隊，避免成為包尾球隊，據内地傳媒報道，今場成敗將決定教練李鐵能否正式獲得帥位。這位一代名將周二憶起兩個職業生涯最美好的時刻。<br />\n<br />\n「一個是2001年10月7日，中國隊獲得2002世界盃決賽周資格；另一個是2002年8月7日，第一次為愛華頓在英超亮相，我完成人生中的夢想，是中國人首次出現在英超。」李鐵說。<br />\n<br />\n如果國足能擊敗港隊，李鐵將正式成為球隊主帥，這是教練生涯最美好的時刻，且看球員們能否助他一臂之力？也有指，今仗將是他最後一次帶領國足，不過一切將由勝負來定。<br />\n<br />\n按國內博彩公司所列出的盤口，國足顯然被看高一線，而有大陸網友在網站留言：「既然他們想要5大訴求，就贏他們5球！」"},{"pid":"687fee71f20142a090c3e75b32387fa1b2f62bc7","tid":1787523,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:44:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/sports/player?newsId=sp27894726180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp27894726180&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BuiKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=01480581\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp27894726180&h=f9f33435\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/sports/player?newsId=sp27894726180</a>"},{"pid":"a5688b55c16757cf92af51f2edee422a7f1db4ec","tid":1787523,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"香港金總終於接受網上會員申請啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6771cf1ecac0ba64bd5384cec11e7a85e7231c01","tid":1787523,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"